A. Beacon Probing (BP)
B. Host Standby Router Protocol (HSRP)
C. Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (BFD)
D. Virtual Router Redundancy Protocol (VRRP)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------> Correct Answer: C
